<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_221_r2l8">Wır dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc . Bekennen . etc . Vmb ſölıch klag vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l9"><expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> als . Dorothea . Dıetreıchs von vvyſentaw elıche <expan>wırtin<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l10">
<del rend="strikethrough">getan hat vnd tut </del> / auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> gut getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l11">hat vnd tut vor dem lantgerıcht des Burggraftums ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l12">Daʒ wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> lıeben <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratgeſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Volkm<ex>eir</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l13">vnd <expan>Stepf<ex>an</ex></expan> Coler . <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l15">gwalt vnd macht / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_221_r2l14"><expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> gut . von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l16"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat . gen Jr ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ʒu ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l17"><expan>trette<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch anleyt wıder ʒu nemen ʒu <expan>gewın<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l18">verluſt vnd ʒu <expan>all<ex>e</ex>m</expan> rechten / Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_221_r2l20"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_221" id="110v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
